WEBVTT

00:11.270 --> 00:12.320
Berani lagi tak?

00:11.550 --> 00:13.880
[1997]

00:13.020 --> 00:14.340
Awak buli adik saya!

00:15.820 --> 00:16.880
Dah tiada apa-apa.

00:17.830 --> 00:18.920
Kenapa kaki awak terluka?

00:18.920 --> 00:20.280
Berhenti! Apa yang berlaku?

00:20.280 --> 00:21.320
Jangan bergaduh lagi!

00:21.320 --> 00:22.320
Apa masalah awak?

00:22.320 --> 00:23.120
Awak tiada apa-apa?

00:23.120 --> 00:24.380
Awak budak kelas mana?

00:24.800 --> 00:25.920
Muda-muda lagi, tak belajar benda baik,

00:25.920 --> 00:27.450
belajar bergaduh pula itu.

00:27.830 --> 00:28.870
Panggil guru kelas awak ke sini.

00:28.870 --> 00:30.730
Dia bergaduh, awak pun tengok saja?

00:30.730 --> 00:32.159
Panggil guru kelas awak ke sini segera!

00:32.159 --> 00:34.160
Tak tahu bercakap secara rasional?

00:34.560 --> 00:35.640
Bergaduh boleh selesaikan masalahkah?

00:35.640 --> 00:36.070
Ayah!

00:36.070 --> 00:37.150
Ayah!

00:37.150 --> 00:38.520
Ayah, jangan pukul mereka.

00:38.520 --> 00:39.710
Jangan pukul abang lagi.

00:39.710 --> 00:40.840
Awak berdiri tegak!

00:41.070 --> 00:42.470
Ayah belum tegur awak lagi.

00:42.470 --> 00:44.200
Pak cik, jangan pukul lagi!

00:44.320 --> 00:45.430
Hal itu tiada kena-mengena dengan mereka.

00:45.430 --> 00:46.670
Budak lelaki itu buli Zhou Jin,

00:46.670 --> 00:47.920
dah jadi tabiat dia.

00:48.070 --> 00:49.880
Kami dah lama bersabar dengannya.

00:49.880 --> 00:51.710
Betul, kami dah lama bersabar dengannya.

00:51.710 --> 00:52.970
Jangan pukulnya lagi.

00:53.200 --> 00:54.200
Jangan banyak bercakap!

00:54.200 --> 00:55.200
Cepat balik ke rumah!

00:55.200 --> 00:57.000
Yan Bin, Zhan Wei,

00:57.110 --> 00:58.110
jangan bercakap.

00:58.600 --> 00:59.640
Cepat pergilah.

01:05.510 --> 01:07.000
Hebat betul awak.

01:08.590 --> 01:10.120
Selalu cari pasal,

01:10.920 --> 01:12.840
awak hampir jadi terkenal di sekolah.

01:12.840 --> 01:13.870
Ayah!

01:14.000 --> 01:16.280
Ayah, jangan pukul abang lagi.

01:16.280 --> 01:18.560
Jangan pukul mereka lagi.

01:18.710 --> 01:20.590
Jangan pukul lagi.

01:21.400 --> 01:22.680
Sudahlah.

01:23.780 --> 01:25.430
Awak ini si pembuat masalah juga,

01:25.430 --> 01:26.840
cepatlah membesar.

01:26.870 --> 01:29.400
Jangan buat abang-abang
risaukan awak lagi.

01:29.810 --> 01:30.670
Berdiri tegak!

02:55.020 --> 03:00.660
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:00.930 --> 03:03.380
[Episod 18]

03:11.360 --> 03:11.960
Sudahlah,

03:12.150 --> 03:13.150
